
# 2025-11-20 14:25:57.001225
+Code the following app
+```
+Empathic MindCheck is a mini-app dedicated to mental well-being, designed to offer a safe, welcoming, and non-judgmental space where users can explore their feelings.
+Through targeted questions, empathetic language, and intuitive tools, the app helps users better understand their emotional state and develop greater awareness of their psychological balance.
+
+The mini-app guides users through short emotional check-ins that assess mood, stress, anxiety, energy, sleep, and need for support. Each interaction is designed to be gentle, reassuring, and respectful: users are free to respond as they wish or skip questions, always maintaining full control of their data.
+
+After each check-in, the app offers personalized feedback, small self-care suggestions (such as breathing exercises or guided micro-reflections), and the option to record thoughts or emotions in a short integrated journal.
+
+Empathic MindCheck is not intended to replace a mental health professional, but offers a simple and human tool to:
+
+reconnect with your emotions
+
+identify patterns of stress or anxiety
+
+find helpful resources in difficult times
+
+track your well-being over time
+```
+
+Generate an app logo and update the app metadata title and description.

